  "page": "Not A Blog",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Not A Blog</b></i> is the personal blog of <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>. Formerly located at <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LiveJournal\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:LiveJournal\">LiveJournal</a>, in April 2018 it was moved to Martin's own website.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Older entries and comments will remain on LiveJournal, but new updates to the blog will be on Martin's site only.\n</p><p>Information presented by Martin in blog entries and comments is considered <a href=\"/index.php/Canon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Canon\">semi-canon</a>, similar to <a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Not_A_Blog&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com\">Not A Blog at LiveJournal</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/\">Not A Blog at georgerrmartin.com</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Not_A_Blog&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Not A Blog: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://grrm.livejournal.com/566320.html\">Not A Blog is moving away...</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template talk:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:ASOIAF&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Derived_works\" title=\"Derived works\">Derived works</a> from the world of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Games</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>Collectibl